
---

**`.gitignore`**  
```gitignore
# Byte-compiled / optimized / DLL files
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# C extensions
*.so

# Distribution / packaging
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/
.eggs/

# Env and config
config/env/*.yaml
config/env/.env
*.env

# Docker
docker-compose.override.yml
.docker/

# Logs and databases
*.log
*.sqlite3
*.db

# Migrations
migrations/versions/*.pyc
migrations/versions/__pycache__/

# IDEs and editors
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*~

# Pytest
htmlcov/
.coverage
.cache
nosetests.xml
coverage.xml
.pytest_cache/

# Celery
celerybeat-schedule
celerybeat.pid

# Virtualenv
venv/
env/
.venv/

# Secrets
*.pem
*.key
